{"tid":620342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢中殺父]日本鹿兒島發生連環命案","createTime":"2018-04-07T13:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T13:26:27.000Z","uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4378e5ae745b4508be750857d1c396e46743f94","tid":620342,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】日本鹿兒島發生連環命案，兩女一男死亡，警方拘捕一名38歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n三名死者伏屍在薩摩川內市這間住所，身上有多處傷痕，死因有待調查，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方拘捕一名38歲無業男子</span>，懷疑同連環命案有關，<span style=\"color: red;\">疑兇沒有交代同住的父親和祖母的去向，但暗示兩人已死亡</span>。<br />\n<br />\n疑兇的父親因為多日沒有上班，公司上星期五聯絡其家人，但<span style=\"color: red;\">前往住所查看的三名親戚和鄰居之後都不知所蹤</span>，警方接報到場後找到三具屍體，正調查犯案動機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=301571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D301571&d=xofnaCHj%2BqiTBLGoIczafo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=95282d39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D301571&h=0f41bcf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=301571</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75bb511324dfe551001b0e5455ac8da7f9670de","tid":620342,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"去嗰個死嗰個"},{"pid":"03e8baf0ea5f7d27ff5d1699b5c4ae7374b6e7d0","tid":620342,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"大和民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4ba37f25d411687ff6b439702ce003f776e0b4","tid":620342,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b36d19aeb69142b34e179345798b2bfa2e598df5","tid":620342,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T13:26:27.00